text: Gerakan Tanah Air (GTA, Homeland Movement or Homeland Party) is a group of Malay political parties started by former Malaysian Prime Minister Mahathir Mohamad in August 2022. Mahathir said GTA would compete in the next election against the ruling Barisan Nasional. The group applied for official registration on 6 September 2022, but did not win any seats in the 2022 General Election. == References == Category:Mahathir Mohamad
title: Gerakan Tanah Air
